OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,FCumbria Police made 20 arrests during
OL,7,Fa week-long crackdown on county lines
OL,8,Fdrugs crime.
OL,10,FThe force says 12 search warrants were
OL,11,Fexecuted, and substances including
OL,12,Fcocaine, ketamine and MDMA were
OL,13,Fseized, alongside weapons and over
OL,14,F#15,000 in cash.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
