CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,FCounty lines drug crimes involve
OL,7,Fmoving drugs from one area to another
OL,8,F- usually across police or local
OL,9,Fauthority boundaries, and often
OL,10,Finvolving by children or vulnerable
OL,11,Fpeople, according to the National
OL,12,FCrime Agency.
OL,14,FOfficers also made arrests for other
OL,15,Foffences discovered while targeting
OL,16,Fdrug crimes, and police undertook work
OL,17,Fto gather intelligence and prevent
OL,18,Fpeople from falling into working for
OL,19,Fcounty lines drug peddlers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,FCumbria Constabulary's
OL,7,F'intensification week' aimed to target
OL,8,Foffenders, safeguard victims, and
OL,9,Fprotect vulnerable people like
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FAs part of the week-long action,
OL,13,Fcocaine, counterfeit cigarettes and
OL,14,Fmore than #3,300 in cash were seized
OL,15,Ffrom a Burton in Kendal property, with
OL,16,Ftwo arrests being made.
OL,18,FA total of #75,000 worth of cocaine
OL,19,Fwas taken over the period across
OL,20,FCumbria.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,FSuspected cannabis, two air pistols
OL,7,Fand a pitbull were taken from a
OL,8,Fproperty in Barrow, with one man being
OL,9,Farrested.
OL,11,FIn Carlisle one man was arrested, and
OL,12,Fsuspected cannabis, cocaine, ketamine
OL,13,Fand cash were seized.
OL,15,FA crossbow, a stun gun, three vehicles
OL,16,Fand 26 phones were also among the
OL,17,Fitems seized.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
