FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Sam Johnson said:
OL,7,F"Tackling county lines drugs crime
OL,8,Fremains a year-long priority for
OL,9,FCumbria Police.
OL,11,F"Our officers are investigating and
OL,12,Faiming to disrupt, deter and detain
OL,13,Fpeople involved in this offending
OL,14,Fevery day.
OL,16,F"Intensification periods such as this
OL,17,Fhelp provide an additional focus and
OL,18,Fshine a spotlight on the issue `
OL,19,Fsending a clear message to those
OL,20,Fintent on causing harm in the process.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,F"At the heart of the county lines
OL,7,Fmodel is the exploitation of
OL,8,Fvulnerable people ` and sometimes
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,F"That is why as well as relentlessly
OL,12,Fpursuing those involved, we also have
OL,13,Fa prevention-first approach to
OL,14,Fstopping this type of offending in the
OL,15,Ffirst place."
OL,17,FCumbria's Police, Fire and Crime
OL,18,FCommissioner, David Allen, said:
OL,19,F"Cumbria has a zero-tolerance policy
OL,20,Fwhen it comes to drugs in our county.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
