OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773504676
OL,3,C20 arrested as part of county drug
OL,4,Clines crackdown
OL,6,F"I am pleased to see Cumbria
OL,7,FConstabulary continue to tackle drugs
OL,8,Fand send out the clear message that
OL,9,Fthere is no place for drug dealers in
OL,10,Fthis county and if you are caught, you
OL,11,Fwill face all the consequences of your
OL,12,Factions."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
